{
    "project": {
        "name": "dlog-project",
        "directory": ".",

    },
    "scan": {
        "directories": ["include", "src", "tests"],

    },

        "log_file": "dlogcover.log",

        "show_uncovered_paths_details": false
    },

            "enabled": true,
            "functions": ["qDebug", "qInfo", "qWarning", "qCritical", "qFatal"],

        },

            "enabled": true,
            "functions": {
                "debug": ["logDebug", "LOG_DEBUG", "LOG_DEBUG_FMT"],
